About

Once upon a time, a little frog name Cat decided to spread joy and laughter beyond his pond. So, he created a cryptocurrency called cat Fun. As more and more people joined the community, the value of Cat Fun grew, and cat's dream of spreading joy throughout the world became a reality. And whenever people thought of cat Fun, they couldn't help but smile and feel a little bit happier.

cat Fun tired of watching everyone play hot potato with the endless derivative ShibaCumGMElonKishuTurboAssFlokiMoon Inu coins. The Inu’s have had their day. It’s time for the most recognizable meme in the world to take his reign as king of the memes. cat is here to make memecoins great again. Launched stealth with no presale, zero taxes, LP burnt and contract renounced, $CAT is a coin for the people, forever. Fueled by pure memetic power, let $CAT show you the way.

WHITEPAPER

How To Buy

Create a Wallet

Download metamask or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktop users, download the google chrome extension by going to metamask.io.

Get Some BNB

Have BNB in your wallet to switch to CAT FUN.

Go to PINKSALE

Connect the pinksale link with your wallet dapp browser and fill the amount of BNB you want to purchase the tokens of CAT FUN

Switch BNB for $CAT FUN

Click on Buy Button to make a purchase and confirm the transaction.

No Taxes, No Bullshit. It’s that simple !!
